reviewText: Love these movies and getting them on one cd is fantastic. I don't mind reviewing, but I do mind telling me how many words I need in a review.
Love Meryl streep and alec baldwin ...great duo working together,..must of watched this movie at least 30 times! Must see
Love both these movies.  arrived earllier then expected. love the music in Momma Mia and anything Meryl Streep is usually good.
Fun movies for a night in.
Very pleased.  Used as a gift.
Enjoyed the movie the scenery and music
happy with these movies, came in a very timely manner!
My high-schooler loves Mama Mia - great deal
I have seen both these movies many times in the past and love them. That's why I bought them this times for Christmas gifts.
Love, love, love these movies. Two great movies in one bundle. Arrived on time and was well packaged.
Both movies are funny and well written.  I enjoyed them both. Meryl Streep is a great actress.

These two films just illustrate the rainbow of talent Meryl Streep offers an audience.  The woman can sing and dance and acts with whatever the role demands.  The cast of both films are marvelous.  They'll become part of my perennial favorites for watching.  Lush backdrops for good stories about growing older.
lots of humor and enjoyable music on one disc
The Movie Mamma Mia did not play.  It got stuck about 8 minutes into the show.  I am rating that I hate it because it doesn't play.
The DVD Arrived on Time. I Like All the Stars of the Two Movies, I Enjoyed watching them. The Price for the Two Movie is Great. I would Recommend it to Every One. Thanks
This was a good deal for the 2 movies. Both movies are so enjoyable with great casts. Very much feel -good flicks.

Great  movie.... Our library copy got stolen !
I then decided to get my own..... There are times
when I need this happy-movie!  :-)
I loved this movie, it was great fun to watch.  The scenery was beautiful.  Great cast.  Can't wait to see the sequel.
product arrived as described and works fine.

My husband and I enjoy ABBAs music so this is a good film for us.  I love Pierce Brosnan and though his singing is poor I still enjoy him in this role.
  Its Complicated is just fun because Meryl Streep and Baldwin are just so likable.
